data.title: DROBAK PORT, NODRK
data.meta_description: Discover the  Port of DROBAK (NODRK) in Viken fylke, Norway. Stay updated on real-time vessel positions, arrivals, and local weather conditions.
data.text: DROBAK is situated in Viken fylke, Norway at coordinates 59.66º, 10.63º in the Norwegian Coast region. This port’s official UN/Locode is NODRK. General Cargo (0%), Tankers (0%) and Passenger Ships (100%), are the vessel types that commonly call at DROBAK. The recorded maximum length of the vessel’s entering DROBAK is 32 meters.
